Undead Scourge

Vampiric Aura
60% chance on hit to gain 13/14/17/20/22/25/29/33% of the damage you do back as health.

Unholy Aura
Spawn with 8/12/16/20/24/28/32/36% increased movement speed.

Levitation
Spawn with 8/16/24/32/40/48/56/64% reduced gravity

Suicide Bomber
When you die you have a 20/30/40/45/50/55/60/70% chance to deal 80/80/90/100/110/120/120/130 damage to all enemies in a 120/120/140/160/170/170/180/180 unit radius.
